    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/f25dbad70927c0f86d5a00c74f7e3be9.avif?t=1732104629\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>我们的监督官不久前收到了几个沉甸甸的箱子，里面装着令人兴奋不已的新装备。有了这个内容包之后，你就可以使用折叠树架和折叠三脚架策划完美的伏击。它们更具隐蔽性，可以显著降低你在狩猎中对环境的影响，同时减轻你的狩猎压力。猎人，快收拾好行装，荒野正在召唤你！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >折叠树架:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/5c30436bd0adabdd83bad06829163e4a.poster.avif?t=1732104629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/5c30436bd0adabdd83bad06829163e4a.webm?t=1732104629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/5c30436bd0adabdd83bad06829163e4a.mp4?t=1732104629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>对于一个训练有素的猎人来说，折叠树架可谓是必备的捕猎利器。拥有了它，你就可以守株待兔，把握绝佳时机将猎物逮个措手不及。为了策划伏击，你需要环视周遭，找到一颗合适的树，将树架放在适当的高度，然后自己再爬到更高的位置。如果你对最初放置树架的位置不大满意，你可以轻松地进行调整或替换。一切都准备好了之后，你只需静待猎物出现，然后抓准时机发动完美一击。另外，树架还可以减少你对周遭环境的影响，大大减轻狩猎压力。 <br><br><strong>配色选择: </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/c7c6429eff065b2b8b64e7a51dd9dd9e.avif?t=1732104629\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>折叠树架共有三种配色可供选择：针叶林、树林和寒带配色。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >折叠三脚架:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/ba63815b9d20575c40062b9178c7762b.poster.avif?t=1732104629\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/ba63815b9d20575c40062b9178c7762b.webm?t=1732104629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/ba63815b9d20575c40062b9178c7762b.mp4?t=1732104629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>折叠三脚架可以360度旋转。有了它，即便周遭没有树木，你也可以获得更好的有利地形。使用三脚架的优势就在于可以环视周遭，帮助你发现更远处的猎物。除此之外，你完全可以保持隐匿状态。它重量较轻且易于设置，可以减轻你的狩猎压力。<br><br><strong>配色选择</strong>: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1076850/extras/07d418b63a7cb15962e85132f6bbeff9.avif?t=1732104629\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>和树架一样，折叠三脚架共有三种配色可供选择：针叶林、树林和寒带配色。",
